#: admin/settings/tour/TTBM_Settings.php:275
msgid "Display settings is somthing that you can use to control frontend display."
msgstr "Mit den Anzeigeeinstellungen können Sie die Frontend-Anzeige steuern."

#: admin/settings/tour/TTBM_Settings.php:276
msgid "You can access it by clicking on the ticket types menu item in the left sidebar"
